T02TD2726E:93b-1: a'ary'a ba lo ki te shva ra sya tsarppa ti ru tsi ta sto tram /
T02TD2726E:93b-3: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyag latsarppa tis bstod pa /
T02TD2726E:93b-4: 'jig rten mgon po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2726E:93b-5: lha mi lha min gyis ni zhabs la btud //
T02TD2726E:93b-6: skye rga na dang 'chi ba rab tu bcom //
T02TD2726E:93b-7: thugs rje'i dang can 'jig rten dbang po khyed //
T02TD2726E:93b-8: skyabs med bdag la snying rje mdzod cig kye //
T02TD2726E:93b-9: nyon mongs rlabs chen tshogs kyis 'joms byed cing //
T02TD2726E:93b-10: sna tshogs sgra sgrogs 'khor ba'i chu gter dbus //
T02TD2726E:93b-11: bying ba bdag ni zung la bsrung bar mdzod //
T02TD2726E:93b-12: brtse ba chen po khyed la bstod par bgyid //
T02TD2726E:93b-13: srid pa'i mun pas mig la nyer 'tshe zhing //
T02TD2726E:93b-14: 'chi ba'i 'jigs pa chen pos lus nyam chung //
T02TD2726E:93b-15: ji srid mnar med mi mnyam 'gro min par //
T02TD2726E:93b-16: bsrung la bcom ldan bdag la kun tu gzigs //
T02TD2726E:93b-17: rtag tu gzhan gyi bud med gzung ba byas //
T02TD2726E:94a-2: bdag gi sdig byas deng du mgon po yis //
T02TD2726E:94a-3: lus can skyon rnams ma lus nyams par mdzod //
T02TD2726E:94a-4: gang zhig 'tsho ba dang ni bkur sti'i phyir //
T02TD2726E:94a-5: bden min 'jig rten 'dod pa min pa smras //
T02TD2726E:94a-6: dmyal ba yun du goms pa'i smra ba can //
T02TD2726E:94a-7: de kun 'jig rten dbang pos zhi bar mdzod //
T02TD2726E:94a-8: bdag gis sems can phan min gang bsams dang //
T02TD2726E:94a-9: gzhan gyis bya la'ang rjes su yi rang pa //
T02TD2726E:94a-10: mgon po de la du bar bgyid pa na //
T02TD2726E:94a-11: deng bdag yid kyi sdig pa bsal du gsol //
T02TD2726E:94a-12: lha dang mi dang lha min ris rnams dang //
T02TD2726E:94a-13: dud 'gro yi dgas dmyal bar 'gro ba nam //
T02TD2726E:94a-14: gnas shing rtag tu gdung ba'i sems can gang //
T02TD2726E:94a-15: khyod ni de rnams bsrung zhes bdag la grags //
T02TD2726E:94a-16: de phyir gzhon nu nying song lus la ni //
T02TD2726E:94a-17: thugs rje'i gzigs pa bdag gi steng spros zhes //
T02TD2726E:94a-18: dmyal bar zhugs pa min pa ji srid du //
T02TD2726E:94a-19: smra bar bgyid yis bcom ldan khyed kyis gson //
T02TD2726E:94a-20: 'on kyang gzhan gyi don la btang snyoms pa //
T02TD2726E:94a-21: dor zhig bcom ldan bdag don ma mdzad do //
T02TD2726E:94a-22: yang na brtse ba'i dbang gyur khyod kyis ni //
T02TD2726E:94a-23: bsod nams bskyed mdzod rgud pa ma gzigs sam //
T02TD2726E:94a-24: dran pas kyang ni khyod ni yongs tshim na //
T02TD2726E:94a-25: sdig pa dor bar mdzod cig ma gzigs sam //
T02TD2726E:94a-26: de slad bcom ldan gzhan phan la mkhas pa //
T02TD2726E:94a-27: bdag ni 'dor bar ma mdzad 'di ru srungs //
T02TD2726E:94a-28: glang chen rta dang bur bcas chung ma dang //
T02TD2726E:94a-29: dmag bcas rgyal srid khang pa sna tshogs dang //
T02TD2726E:94a-30: sha rus mgo dang phrag gi mthar thug pa //
T02TD2726E:94a-31: don du gnyer la mtha' dag khyod kyis byin //
T02TD2726E:94a-32: su zhig 'jig rten dbang po khyod mnyes byad //
T02TD2726E:94a-33: ri lu mig sman mchil lham grub pa dang //
T02TD2726E:94a-34: grub pa'i sman dang nor bu rnam dag sngags //
T02TD2726E:94a-35: gnod sbyin mo dang grong 'jug sgrub par byed //
T02TD2726E:94a-36: gang dag mig dang rkang lag smras pa yi //
T02TD2726E:94a-37: sna tshogs nad kyis 'jig rten nyam thag pa //
T02TD2726E:94a-38: khyod mnyes na ni de rnams yongs rgyas lus //
T02TD2726E:94a-39: rnam sgeg nad med yon tan zab mor 'gyur //
T02TD2726E:94a-40: khyod dgyes gang lags rgyal 'gyur ga ru da //
T02TD2726E:94a-41: gcan gzan gza' dang mkha' 'gro rnam 'byor ma //
T02TD2726E:94a-42: rtag tu zhi 'gyur de yi mdun du ni //
T02TD2726E:94b-0: gshin rje'i pho nya rgyu bar mi byed @94b do //
T02TD2726E:94b-1: 'jig rten dbang phyug dgyes bzhin skyabs med bdag /'dor ba ci zhes bcom ldan bdag smre ste //
T02TD2726E:94b-2: nyi ma so sor lag pa bsgreng byas nas //
T02TD2726E:94b-3: tshig 'khrugs pa yi skrag bzhi bar mdzod //
T02TD2726E:94b-4: 'khrugs pa'i lus kyis song ba'i skye bar bdag / yul drug la ni dbang po g-yo ba'i yid /
T02TD2726E:94b-5: sdig pa mang byas 'dir ni ma lus pa //
T02TD2726E:94b-6: dbres pa'i rgyu yis 'khor zhing rnam par 'dzings //
T02TD2726E:94b-7: gang gis ngan song sdug bsngal ma myong bar //
T02TD2726E:94b-8: bde 'gror mngon sum 'gro de khyed kyis mdzod //
T02TD2726E:94b-9: deng bdag 'jig rten dbang la phyag dang zhing //
T02TD2726E:94b-10: sna tshogs thal sbyar 'di ni phyag gi'o //
T02TD2726E:94b-11: khyod ni rmongs dang sdad pa 'jig pa'i rgyu //
T02TD2726E:94b-12: 'khor ba'i chu gter chen po'i zam pa lags //
T02TD2726E:94b-13: ltung zhing skrag pa slod ba'i dpung pa khyod //
T02TD2726E:94b-14: sdig lci mtshan mor byed pa'i sgra gcan no //
T02TD2726E:94b-15: bla med bde gshegs kyis gsungs de nyis kyis //
T02TD2726E:94b-16: khyod kyis sems can sdug bsngal mang po bskyang //
T02TD2726E:94b-17: rgyal dka' yid srubs bdud las khyod rgyal te //
T02TD2726E:94b-18: kun tu grol ba srid mtsho'i pha rol lo //
T02TD2726E:94b-19: nad kun gcod par mdzad pa khyod kyi sku //
T02TD2726E:94b-20: ma lus 'gro bar mchog tu lus mdzes pa //
T02TD2726E:94b-21: bcom ldan dpe med snying rje'i sin dhu khyod //
T02TD2726E:94b-22: rgyu med gnyen du skye bo rnams la grags //
T02TD2726E:94b-23: rol pas dbang po 'joms shing rnam par byed //
T02TD2726E:94b-24: khyod ni yul la kun nas chags pa 'dor //
T02TD2726E:94b-25: lha yi bsam gtan mnyan bzhag khyod kyi thugs //
T02TD2726E:94b-26: nor ni slong ba po dang thun mong lags //
T02TD2726E:94b-27: brtse ldan khyod nig zhan la phan mdzad kyang //
T02TD2726E:94b-28: gti mug lto 'phye chen pos sos zin cing //
T02TD2726E:94b-29: yul la kun rtog dge ba las ltung ba //
T02TD2726E:94b-30: bdag ni tshim par mi mdzad ci ltar lags //
T02TD2726E:94b-31: mtha' dag 'gro ba'i don bsten snying rje gang //
T02TD2726E:94b-32: khyod kyis spros de nges pa lags sam ci //
T02TD2726E:94b-33: khyod kyi spyan sngar sna tshogs sgra sgrogs pa'i //
T02TD2726E:94b-34: sdig ldan bdag la gang las bsrung mi mdzad //
T02TD2726E:94b-35: mgon khyod snying rje nam mkha' las yangs te //
T02TD2726E:94b-36: sems can rnams la chu 'dzin chu rgyun ltar //
T02TD2726E:94b-37: mya ngan chu dang mtho dma'i yul kun tu //
T02TD2726E:94b-38: ma lus nyin mtshan par med 'bab par 'gyur //
T02TD2726E:94b-39: bcom ldan dag las bdag gis bsod nams gang //
T02TD2726E:94b-40: de ni 'gro 'dis bde blag thob gyur te //
T02TD2726E:94b-41: dpal ldan po ta la yi ri bor gnas //
T02TD2726E:95a-1: tshogs rol pas skye bar shog /'phags pa 'jig rten dbang phyug gi bstod pa grub thob chen po tsarppa tis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2726E:95a-3: // / rgya gar shar phyogs kyi pandi ta chen po nags kyi rin chen gyi zhal snga nas dang /
T02TD2726E:95a-4: lo ts'a ba 'gos gzhon nu dpal gyis bsgyur ba'i//
